###############
### VCP-CMA ### 
###############

*** Automation - faster resource provisioning, more consistency, minimization of human error, scalability/repeatability
          vRA (vRealize Automation) - cloud management platform, automates the provisioning of IT infrastructure, with/without self-service, including approval chain

*** Components
          Cloud Assembly - assembles VMs/Instances into Blueprint
          Service Broker - creates Self-Service catalog
          Orchestrator - scripting
          Code Stream - CI/CD

*** Architecture
          vRLCM + VIDM + vRA
          
